title: Connect to Quickemu Vm Using SSH
tags: @zettel _method ssh quickemu
roam-id: 93faa1c9-a52c-4eae-a1b3-a29d386eb3c3
type: text/markdown

- don\'t attempt to change the IP of your guest. just use the following

  ``` bash
  ssh -p 22220 your_user@localhost
  ```

- note that you must use `localhost` and not the guest IP address
